{"tid":1077121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又撞！載150人噴射飛航撞中區海濱","createTime":"2019-03-25T11:17:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T11:51:39.000Z","uid":176442,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c406b13f5628d28cd5da6308acabda5c5184ec63","tid":1077121,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190325&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59410364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190325%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59410364&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbqwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=3b53c102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190325%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59410364&h=8c1c5bc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190325&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59410364</a>"},{"pid":"51e1373e09a52efa457fa9a9367a2169b8fb8001","tid":1077121,"uid":176442,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"【船撞碼頭】載有150人噴射飛航引擎故障　撼中西區海濱長廊碼頭<br />\n<br />\n一艘來往港澳的噴射飛航，今日（25日）於中西區海濱長廊碼頭懷疑失控，撞向4號碼頭。現場所見，碼頭石壆碎開，岸上的圍欄被撞至彎曲，有三塊玻璃損毀，一塊更完全爆裂，留下一個大洞。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的噴射飛航由信德中旅營運，據現場一名保安表示，事發下午3時許，他正於更亭當值，突然有途人及清潔工通知他，有船撞向碼頭，並橫掃碼頭石壆，而涉事船長馬上將船駛離現場。<br />\n<br />\n信德中旅營運回覆表示，一艘載有140名乘客及10名船員高速客船宇航2014號，今日下午2時50分從澳門開往上環，約4時於西環對開位置，左邊推進器入水口吸入垃圾，須進行清理工作，惟右邊引擎剛巧出現故障，船隻被水流影響靠向西環岸邊，與岸邊欄杆發生輕微碰撞，致船身油漆脫落。船長隨即作出廣播，並派員視察客艙及乘客情況，確認所有乘客及船員均無恙。船隻在公司拖船協助下於四時十九分返回港澳碼頭。事故已通報有關當局作出進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，下午4時許接獲報案指，西區副食品批發市場對開有船撞壆，碼頭位置有鐵欄受損，事件中無人受傷，警方到達時船已離開，案件列「有財物損毀」，有待進一步調查。"},{"pid":"e60d09c7534a8443254267a505a101410c84c5ba","tid":1077121,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:40:59.000Z","msg":"好驚下次係飛機失事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460c5f26d39cdc82a9ca40ecb79aa1a9324db478","tid":1077121,"uid":173271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"一日一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50ed8e8116774f47108f3ba75697fe505d6bdaf","tid":1077121,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dea0b186fe04d3c634857191c0076d1207d72d8","tid":1077121,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18af971db5e19cc4552c4a0da99d13737d00c429","tid":1077121,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:44:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"491a84577ffa5e8b45a6e92db99772700f5bb4c5","tid":1077121,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5dea0b186fe04d3c634857191c0076d1207d72d8","tid":1077121,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:44:59.000Z","msg":"烏鴉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dead18d03d1ff00fedf14a4d6252c36f8e60f877","tid":1077121,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:46:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba6b6483a6c5120a9e96282f620d212d16745972","tid":1077121,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"水星逆行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac6f860cc553271c95937bb50d89b10206176b3","tid":1077121,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba6b6483a6c5120a9e96282f620d212d16745972","tid":1077121,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"水星逆行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:50:05.000Z","msg":"可能係水星號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe112f3ba5fb18468184ebb6e5910117f330bc8","tid":1077121,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"搭船咁危險，以後取消發牌只準用港豬噢爛橋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}